title: Chocolate and red wine cake
ingredients: ['250g plain flour', '60g cocoa powder', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '225g unsalted butter', '300g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '350ml red wine']
